(1, 'Ecommerce Integration-Soft Launch', 'Deliver a fully operational E-Commerce ecosystem by integrating Salesforce (Commerce & Marketing Cloud) with D-365 ERP and Clientele in Retail POS - delivered in two phases - to drive digital revenue, customer loyalty and an enhanced in-store experience including self-checkout.', 'EBS/ERP Integration', 'Imad Najibeddine', 'Critical', 'Delayed', 'UAT', NULL, '2025-12', '2026-05', '80', 0, 'High', 'Included in initial ERP implementation scope', 'SF Partner - UAT instance + Development completion', 'UAT instance not ready and SF Partner development incomplete - testing cannot begin until both are delivered', 'SF Partner committed delivery by 14-April-2026. Daily status updates/calls scheduled to track progress', '1. ERP–eCommerce integration is on track; however, the overall project timeline has been delayed. Go-live date has been pushed back due to master data readiness issues. 2. UAT sign-off pending', '1. Confirm UAT readiness delivery date from SF Partner. 2. Prepare integration test cases and complete testing by April 25. 3. Prepare for go-live readiness by April 30.'),
